<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Blog Home</title>
  <style>
    /* Minimalist CSS Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Base Styles */
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #fafafa;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Layout */
    header {
      padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      background-color: #fff;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .section-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .section:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    }

    /* Typography */
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #222;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #222;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      color: #555;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Links */
    a {
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #666;
    }

    nav a {
      position: relative;
      padding: 0.3rem 0;
    }

    nav a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #333;
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* Buttons */
    .cta-buttons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      border-color: #999;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.8rem;
        align-items: center;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      .cta-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      
      .section {
        padding: 1.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/add-blog">Add Blog</a>
      <a href="/show">View Blogs</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="intro">
      <h1>Welcome to Our Blog</h1>
      <p>A space for thoughtful writing and meaningful connections. Share your perspective with a community that values authentic expression.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/add-blog" class="btn">Create a New Post</a>
        <a href="/show" class="btn">Browse All Posts</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-grid">
      <div class="section">
        <h2>Why Start Blogging?</h2>
        <p>Blogging helps you express your thoughts, share your knowledge, build an audience, and even improve your writing skills.</p>
        <p>Whether it's tech, travel, lifestyle, or personal stories â€” your voice matters.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Featured Topics</h2>
        <p>Explore popular blogs on technology, motivation, daily life hacks, health tips, and more.</p>
        <p>Our writers share unique content every day to keep you inspired.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Click "Create a New Post", write your content, and publish. It's that simple!</p>
        <p>Your post will be instantly visible to the community.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
        <p>Whether you're here to write or just read, you're welcome. Leave comments, connect with authors, and be part of something meaningful.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>